Believe System(Streaming)
==========================================================
A System that contains the set of rules/procedures/guidelines/arrangements/track/path...so on.. to maintain some special order of objects.
Believe is a single thread that run in believe system.

Believe system is a bundle of understanding that made by lives by using their understanding/feeling by adjusting their previous understanding. This believe system drive one's life.

If one's believe system is poor their life automatically is under hindrance and their movement of life is poor.
If one's believe system is strong their life automatically move with confident.

***Hindrance or confident both are a part of fear only***

How does believe streaming(birth to death)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
First believe(the base of building believe)
-----------------------------
Child age
------------
When child take birth, They don't have any believe/believe system.As they grow they get experience many things in their environment either by self or by some guidelines. At this place only they get concrete or hindered believe.
That is the base of believe and that is the matter.In other words the first believe of any stuff is the base of further believe on that matter.

Ex-
A child touch fir first time and it get burn its finger. This is its self experience and make a concrete believe about fire behavior.

A child without touch the fire its get guideline don't touch fire your finger will get burn.It keep in memory about the fire behavior.

Above both are the first experiences of fire and these experiences take lead for further believe on fire behavior.

***A latter of believe write on empty paper is not easy to erase latter***

Young age
------------
At this age the believe system also become young and they operate based on their faithful for life or there are meaning of believe so that it can balance/enhance their life better.

At this age brain had trained somewhat, at this age one believe on something by adjusting the previous believe(base of believe) or any new believe come in brain with some careful so that it couldn't create any problem in further life.

Ex-
Every one connect with some one have some meaning, there are something that make the connection between them.

Old age
----------
At this age one have some what more experience by hurting them self's many time. This experience make believe that every one have own meaning but this believe system is just the erasing and rewriting on previous written believe...ie paper is not empty but one erase and write on them..
ie here also they have some meaning in their believe system.  

***Believe/believe system is not empty***

***Believe is stumbling block for inner journey*** 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spiritual believe(finally the death of believe system)
---------------------------------------------
When the yogis/sadhak are on their inner journey, they get many experiences on their trek. These experiences make their believe/believe system. These believe system always keep their life in healing mode and the feeling of healing lead their life.

After many many year of trekking their believe system get very concrete/solidity on a particular stuff..specially almighty/Creation/god/nature....so on.
Ie their believe system is centralized completely, all most all believe pass through single believe.

After the perfection on that particular believe the explosion happen on that believe that erase all the believe/believe system.
At this stage human don't try to come out from silence.       
   
 ***Neither any thing to be believe nor to be discard...let them come and go***
